answers.text:
1. Visit www.kfcb.go.ke , E-Services/TMS, 
2. Log into your account and select Apply for a Filming Licence 
3. Fill the application form and attach the required documents; 
4. Accept Terms and Conditions; 
5. The system bills and prompts you to make payment; 
6. Make payment and submit the application for processing; 
7. Application is reviewed and approved; and 
8. Download a FILMING LICENCE and RECEIPT from your account.
